law.text:
The board shall promulgate administrative regulations in accordance with KRS Chapter 13A to:
Establish educational requirements for credentialing as a dialysis technician;
Establish required standards for training programs for dialysis technicians;
Establish credentialing requirements for dialysis technicians;
Establish provisions for discipline of dialysis technicians;
Establish fees for initial credentialing, renewal of credentials, reinstatement of credentials, and other fees as may be necessary, for dialysis technicians; and
Further regulate, as necessary, dialysis technicians.
